## Handoff Receiving Template

```
=== CHATGPT HANDOFF PACKAGE ===
Project: [name]
Handed off from: [platform] ([phase])
Receiving: ChatGPT ([phase])

[Paste into Custom Instructions or project system prompt if ongoing work]
You are working on [project name]. Context: [2-sentence description].
Your role: [specific role]. Key constraints: [constraints].

---

You are continuing work on [project name]. Here is the full context:

## Current Goal
[One sentence outcome]

## What Exists
[Artifacts — name, type, location, status]

## Decisions Made
- [Decision]: [choice] — Reason: [why]

## Context to Preserve
[Key constraints, established context, tone/format requirements]

## Your Task
[Explicit instruction — first, second, third]

## Must Not Change
[Hard constraints]

## Tools to Enable
[Web search / code execution / file analysis — whatever this task needs]

## Re-Entry
When complete or blocked, provide:
- Summary of what was produced
- Files or outputs created
- Any decisions made
- Any blockers
This will be used to run: /handoff return from ChatGPT

=== END ===
```

## Configuration Checklist
- [ ] Enable web search if real-time data is needed
- [ ] Enable code execution if the task involves running or validating code
- [ ] Use a Project if this is ongoing work (maintains file context)
- [ ] Paste Custom Instructions context if not using a Project
- [ ] For computer use tasks: confirm GPT-5.4+ is selected
